Thanks <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/useverinewolfe.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Severine Wolfe</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/white_fire.gif BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Evoker</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(6/28/01 11:26:58 pm)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://www.clan-donald.com/screenshots/severine.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Confirm Multiquesting...</span><hr size=1> The only part of this that I have multiquested was the stripping of the potion and handing it in to Arandir.  I got the note I needed for the gnome in BB and subsequently the oil from the Golem in Fear and the Staff of Gabstick.<br>
