</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uzaknalfien.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Zaknalfien</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(6/30/01 12:14:22 pm)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://www.iwdesign.net/everquest/images/small_sig.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Confirm Multiquesting...</span><hr size=1> I multied the BCS. The only sticker is the faction level. A friend of mine had everything except the BCS as well, and lost all the parts because the bard who had the staff was using a faction song to get to high enough faction...but the song wore off during turnin.<br>
<br>
That's why the best bet is to have the other player begin the trade, wait until you invis them, then continue, as no part of the wizard epic requires Indiff faction, and invis will bump you to indiff.<br>
<br>
But in general, whoever turns in the LAST part to the wizard epic to Arantir gets the bag, if everybody involved had the right faction. <p><img src="http://www.iwdesign.net/everquest/images/sig.jpg"></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uthistlenote.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Thistlenote</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(7/1/01 12:41:42 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Confirm Multiquesting...</span><hr size=1> Can anyone confirm multi-questing BCS?  I looted one on a recent Phini raid because no wizzies were present.  I'd really like to know exactly how it was done before I go and potentially destroy a guildie's hard earned epic loots.<br>
<br>
Thanks,<br>
<br>
Thistlenote<br>
60th Bard of Saryrn<br>
Arc of Amicus <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uaemoonlanys.showPublicProfile?language=EN>AemoonLanys</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(7/1/01 9:48:50 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Confirm Multiquesting...</span><hr size=1> FYI Mr. Bard, do NOT depend on your song for faction. It most likely will wear off during the hand-in, leaving you lower faction needed, destroying 3 staves. Just hand in your staff to Arantir 1st, get a invis, hit trade. Other wiz hands in 2 other staves. Wiz gets some crappy weapon with effect <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uarbaalscalebane.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Arbaal Scalebane</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC=http://www.harmonium.net/pics/hatt.jpg BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Channeler</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(7/1/01 3:07:32 pm)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://www.harmonium.net/pics/hatt.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Confirm Multiquesting...</span><hr size=1> After I completed my Epic, I won another Gnarled Staff on a pickup VS. I had a friend who needed it so I offered to multiquest with her. (Btw, when you finish epic your TrueSpirit faction drops to Dubiously).<br>
<br>
We went up to Halas, she spawned Arantir with the note, I put the staff in trade window, she invissed me, she put the staves in trade window. I gave, she gave, she got the pack.<br>
<br>
It works the same way with any of the staves. <p><a href=http://eq.castersrealm.com/players/view_profile.asp?Id=7974>[60 Sorcerer] Arbaal McOwn (Erudite) Remedy ZONE:  Ezboard</a></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uaemoonlanys.showPublicProfile?language=EN>AemoonLanys</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(7/1/01 8:45:07 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Confirm Multiquesting...</span><hr size=1> nod, MQ still works, just got mine <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p><body>

