<br>
HUGE thank-you to Rosanna for chaining her Phin staff.<br>
<br>
We both went up to Halas.  In his merchant form he was indiff to both of us.  After I turned in the note and Arantir spawned, he conned appr to us both.  She turned in the phin staff - no invis.  So we had a bit of a panic attack as he didn't say anything at that point.  With a pounding heart, I turned in my two.<br>
<br>
[Tue Jul 24 02:38:55 2001] Arantir Karondor says 'Here, this pack contains all of our items.  You will never be able to open it again, so you must deliver the pack, intact, to Solomen.  He will then reward you.  Now that I have helped you, leave me in peace. <br>
[Tue Jul 24 02:38:55 2001] Your faction standing with Truespirit got better.<br>
<br>
And, viola, I got the bag.<br>
<br>
BTW, I wasn't sure if anyone had done this, but I cast identify on the bag before I turned it in:<br>
[Tue Jul 24 02:48:18 2001] Item Lore: Godlike magic radiates from this bag.<br>
<br>
Before I turned in the bag:<br>
[Tue Jul 24 02:47:17 2001] You say, 'Hail, Solomen'<br>
[Tue Jul 24 02:47:18 2001] Solomen says 'Ah, I see you have found my study.  This is where I study and scribe the history of magic in Norrath. <br>
[Tue Jul 24 02:48:33 2001] Solomen says 'You actually did it!  I never would have thought that anyone could have truly followed this path.  This is a tribute to your intelligence and patience.  Here, take this staff and know that you have made Solusek Ro and all the wizards of the world proud this day. <br>
[Tue Jul 24 02:48:33 2001] Your faction standing with Truespirit got better.<br>
<br>
And then:<br>
[Tue Jul 24 03:00:09 2001] Solomen glowers at you dubiously -- You could probably win this fight.<br>
[Tue Jul 24 03:00:12 2001] You say, 'Hail, Solomen'<br>
[Tue Jul 24 03:00:12 2001] Solomen says 'I didn't know Slime could speak common..go back to the sewer before I lose my temper.'<br>
[Tue Jul 24 03:00:31 2001] Rosanna says, 'Hail, Solomen'<br>
[Tue Jul 24 03:00:31 2001] Solomen says 'Ah, I see you have found my study.  This is where I study and scribe the history of magic in Norrath. <br>
[Tue Jul 24 03:00:42 2001] You say, 'what history of magic?'<br>
[Tue Jul 24 03:00:42 2001] Solomen says 'Oh look..a talking lump of refuse..how novel!'<br>
